# Kansei

Kansei is the local control plane for AI-assisted research operations.

## Operating Rules

- Project registries live in `projects.toml`.
- Provider registries live in `providers.toml`.
- Durable private memory lives in `knowledge/`.
- Daily and weekly operating surfaces live in `dashboards/`.
- Reusable procedures live in `runbooks/`.
- Agent task prompts live in `prompts/`.

Update managed harness files with `kansei update-harness`.

